Motion,Shadow,is,a,system,of,wearable,flexible,fabric,with,embedded,sensors,that,is,used,to,digitally,capture,motion,The,Motion,Shadow,API,allows,to,integrate,D,motion,in,real,time,with,wearables,hardware,and,software,Documentation,guides,developers,to,work,with,the,motion,interface,connect,to,Wi,Fi,network,and,interact,with,a,viewer,that,displays,graphics,in,real,time,The,API,offers,XML,format,and,is,compatible,with,C,C,Lua,Unity,and,Maya,functions